c: 23
v: 44
t: "thm 'arsalna rusulana 'iilaa tilk al'umam yatabie bedhm bedana, kulama daea rasul amth kdhbwh, fa'atbaena baedahum bedana balhlak waldmar, walam yabq 'iilaa 'akhbar hlakhm, wajaealnaha 'ahadith liman bedhm, ytkhdhwnha ebrt, fhlakana wsuhqana liqawm laa yusadiqun alrusul wala ytyewnhm"